Headshot Birthday Pop
Just adds the grunt birthday party effect when getting a killing headshot on a player (For the weapon projectiles that are flagged as such)
Newbie
1.0
Multiplayer

## Head section
EditTag objects\characters\elite\mp_elite\mp_elite.model
SetField NewDamageInfo[0].DamageSections[1].InstantResponses[0].SecondaryTransitionEffect objects\characters\grunt\fx\grunt_birthday_party.effect
SaveTagChanges
Exit

